# Introducing Dectraced

Welcome to the official Dectraced blog.

Dectraced is a technology-focused team created to research online threats, improve security awareness, and work together on technical projects.

This blog will be used for sharing updates, project progress, reports, and other information related to our work.

## What We Do

Dectraced focuses on:

- Researching and documenting online threats
- Improving security knowledge
- Building technology projects
- Sharing useful information with the community

## What To Expect

Future posts will include:

- Team updates
- Project announcements
- Technical articles
- Research reports

Thank you for visiting the Dectraced website. More updates will be posted soon.
